quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,98,"Kune here guta rakatenda (mushure mokuona marwadzo), uye kutenda kwaro (munguva iyoyo) kukaribatsira (kubva mumarwadzo)? (Mhinduro hapana), kunze kwevanhu vaJonah pavakatenda, takavabvisira marwadzo anonyadzisa muhupenyu wepanyika, uye tikavabvumidza kuti vafare kwenguva diki"
  10,99,"Uye dai Tenzi vako vaida, avo vari munyika dai vakatenda vose pamwechete. Saka (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) uchamanikidza here vanhu, kusvika vave vatendi"
  10,100,"Hazvisi kumunhu kutenda, kunze nekuda kwaAllah, uye vachaisa hasha dzavo kune avo vasina hanya"
  10,101,"Iti: “Tarisai zvese zviri mumatenga nemunyika,” asi hapana zviratidzo kana vayambiri vanobetsera avo vasingatendi.”"
  10,102,"Nokudaro vakamirira here (chimwe chinhu) kunze (kwekuparadzwa) kwemazuva evarume vakapfuura mushure mavo? Iti: “Nokudaro mirirai, ndiripowo pane avo vakamirira.”"
  10,103,Nokudaro (mushure) takanunura vatumwa vedu neavo vanotenda! Ndozvazviri zvinomanikidzirwa kwatiri kununura vatendi
  10,104,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Imi vanhu! Kana musingagutsikane nechitendero changu (Islaam), nokudaro (zivai kuti) handifi ndakanamata izvo zvamunonamata kunze kwaAllah. Asi ndinonamata Allah vanoita kuti mufe, uye ndakakomekedzwa kuti ndive umwe wevatendi.”"
  10,105,"“Uye (zvadzikiswa kwandiri): ‘Tendeudza huso hwako (Muhammad (SAW)) kuchitendero cheHaneef (Islaam, kunamatwa kwaMwari mumwechete), uye zvirokwazvo usava umwe wemaMushrikoon (avo vanosanganisa Mwari nezvimwe zvinhu mukunamata).’"
  10,106,"‘Uye usava unodana chimwe chinhu kunze kwaAllah icho chisingakubatsiri kana kukukuvadza, asi kana ukadaro, zvirokwazvo uchava umwe wemaDhaalimoon (vanosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu mukunamata uye vatadzi).’”"